Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說小美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼時候才動手寫做作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不做完可不能吃點心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,背好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千幫我撓撓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己不會撓啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛好是手夠不到的地方  快點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這裡嗎？哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  再往下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再下面點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,往左點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  就是這
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夠不到這裡才怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  千佳  這裡有些不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.77,0:00:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.06,0:00:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我不是叫你撓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰管你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真累
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那姐姐幫我撓背
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:00:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫個正五角形
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算出其中一個角的度數…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  我自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說  你這不是夠得著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  我去拿抹布過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小美先用抽紙擦一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.25,0:01:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓你擤鼻涕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯  對不起  千佳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來做個逗趣的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,餃子耳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鼻子裡的抽紙算怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是54度  那這個角就是它的兩倍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那吃點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.57,0:01:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼都沒動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也做點作業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總有佈置論文什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你連這個都不清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  我不吐槽了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是伸惠姐的作風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把紙給我拿掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又調過我遊戲的時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,經常同樣的景色會玩厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別再動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千真是小心眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要溫柔對待禁煙者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你是三分鐘熱度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  要賭賭看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是禁煙成功了  可以讓你每天第一個泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你要拿什麼賭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:23.86,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,『明天再見』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是週三啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是週三啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天有體育課嗎  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天有體育課嗎  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  你又在玩啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  你又在玩啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別學我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別學我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,買東西去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,約翰  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  不是你所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是惡作劇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是至交呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒頭沒腦地你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友和至交有區別嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然有區別啊…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不確定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至交是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是在問你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  去問伸惠姐看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服上沾著線頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很大一條
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼邋遢難怪沒男朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千倒茶來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐能讓一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要聽CD
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂等等  剛剛的話題還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便哪個都行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐我問你啊  朋友和至交不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟學校的朋友發郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友好歹還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人不是至交而是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至交…不對  朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至交？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至交是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我這不是在問你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茉…茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜  照我說的去做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就在茉莉的額頭上寫個「神」字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…真卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  要我怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把鼻毛拔下來接到睫毛上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好濃密～睫毛增毛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說這句
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還不快做  「好濃密～」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  換別的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！茉莉變成什麼樣都無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放開茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把手指插到安娜鼻孔裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那  我就親安娜了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你個卑鄙的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要寫了  我真的寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在搞什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛在進行測試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關…關於什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,測試安娜和茉莉感情有多好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是出來保護她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪姐姐來搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜肯定不會照做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「睫毛好濃密～」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事誰會做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也沒來救安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒必要救她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是小菜一碟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…我不想和這種人交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你安娜  剛剛保護了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  這是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們感情真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是至交嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是至交  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,具體哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學校裡在一起  在家也一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手機上貼著一樣的大頭貼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有  經常互發郵件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小千也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你們都發什麼內容的郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就看最新的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘛  好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是睡了抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的測試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍有些不安呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜有把握嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太自信…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但茉莉讀書很用功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相信自己沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一下子信心百倍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到學校再一起復習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可笑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快看啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是至交嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛啊～是至交吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  就讓你們看看我和小千的郵件內容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肋骨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,折斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千佳真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼看我們才是至交嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說是安娜她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  我們明天也有國語測試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的測試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍稍有點不安哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千不擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  果然很噁心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概因為發件人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們自稱是至交
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發展到什麼程度了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和小千都親過了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還互相揉過胸！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是很久之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  我們才是至交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千小千
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是真百合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「真百合」是英文？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,別打擾我啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉你還是不知道為好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你們是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起朋友和至交…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺更像是老大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:02.26,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（怎麼形容呢…感覺像老大？）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老大…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是嘛  我沒有至交
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  姐姐  我們也是至交啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用安慰了  我老你們這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個嘛  雖然年齡上有些差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺想睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太理解年齡差距什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我最喜歡姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神來吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有你們在我就無憾了～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,復活得好快啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千和你是至交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,某種意義上來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  比起安娜她們  我們這邊感情要更好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你較什麼勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…安娜患了重病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打個比方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:14:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不從別人那裡接受移植就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  茉莉你會怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那樣做的話  我會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛  不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然會捐出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死啊  安娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  都說了是打比方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別哭了別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果茉莉你有個萬一我也會捐給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  謝謝安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千小千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  這次又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把你內臟拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這穿越得也太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  算了  晚上再聽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦小千
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我得了重病
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接受移植手術才能存活的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  什麼亂七八糟的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你會怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給了你我會怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…那會給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎  謝謝你  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡你了  我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我真的覺得美羽和千佳感情好好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,配合默契
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人到達的境界真讓人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  果然我和小千是舉世無雙的至交啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  這樣夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我不會把內臟給你就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是給啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  承蒙關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,How to despair combo？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:15:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Comple…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Completely
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正確
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太鬆散了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們太鬆散了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好青年怎麼能每天過同一種生活模式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還不是每天從窗口進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說是怎樣相同的模式嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來學小千
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小美  你吃了我的布丁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭死小美了  滾一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回自己家睡去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎每天都這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全是你害的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面是茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡借我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始學茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停下來吧  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇  姐姐抱抱～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣  這些的罪魁禍首都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽  把眼鏡還我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…不是這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個  來學安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  肚子餓扁扁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…學安娜最累人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始提問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好  我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨我最喜歡可愛的女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  伸惠姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想說明什麼？啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也…也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如蛹變蝶  佐竹變老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.37,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  佐竹是狗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上就升國中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了迎接那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍要做些心理準備才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,國中生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Junior high school
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別胡說  美羽！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉和安娜永遠是小學生～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個不能理她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但突然說要做心理準備也沒什麼好做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  先從外形上開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到國中生就想到制服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先把情緒調動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是我的舊校服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  怎麼姐姐也換上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真煩  你有意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,升入國中就要穿校服上學了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是有些害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是穿這個要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只想穿上試試
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我們升級後的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個都能看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,南無南無  制服制服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,從各個方面來說你都是危險人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了  大家成為了國中生的未來世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小美～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（先走一步）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要…要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,國二  伊藤千佳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然修得了飛簷走壁的本領
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到如今仍毫無出眾之處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  千佳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻木茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為留…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因某種不可告人的秘密  現在還讀小學六年級
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好遲啊  小千  還有小六
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別…別再這麼叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又睡懶覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小千你真散漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫小美你不來叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別總想著依靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說這種話嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我依然這麼出色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是柯波拉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噓  會被她聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,國一  安娜·柯波拉·BlackCustom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是逃課慣犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安娜啊  你能念出這個來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金…金…戈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讀作Ginger Ale（薑汁汽水）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安…安娜～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也沒能走到教室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃課記錄又更新了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我還是很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐竹長成了一隻雄壯的老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而伸惠姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這不是小美嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖  很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小美太可愛了  喜歡死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從安娜她們離去的悲傷中走出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為我的寵物開始了第二段人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的小鎮又是和平的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這餅乾太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  不愧是千佳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完還有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（二手特價  已售  ￥27000  僅限現貨）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易把錢攢下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只差一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就等不到發薪水的日子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快看快看  從今天起海上活動開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候開始戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是那種遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抽煙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抽一根又不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太勉強自己對健康不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有說服力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別說你忘了我們的約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.02,0:23:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.23,0:23:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在去？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.07,0:23:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是上週加的油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.08,0:23:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  可以借一下車子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要去通知大家～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（茉莉的手機）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  茉莉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說啊  雖然事出突然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.30,0:23:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我去問問安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在千佳家集合吧  我馬上動身
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點不著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,（約定  打賭輸了  就帶我去海邊！）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海啊  海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.73,0:24:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海啊  海啊  海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.07,0:24:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.12,0:24:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.92,0:24:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.09,0:24:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.21,0:24:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.84,0:24:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  找到了有趣的貝殼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.05,0:24:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有透明的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.22,0:24:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.14,0:24:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現螃蟹了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.26,0:24:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,螃蟹？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.89,0:24:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.81,0:25:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.73,0:25:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不會厭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.69,0:25:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣的波浪湧來又退回
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.70,0:25:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大點的浪都不來一個
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.83,0:25:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.00,0:25:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是裝酷的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.54,0:25:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連內褲都濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.13,0:25:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把車子坐墊弄濕了爸爸可是會發火的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.17,0:25:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼大了還尿濕  真丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.93,0:25:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.09,0:25:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.35,0:25:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住站住站住！
